com.adobe.granite.workflow.event

Class WorkflowEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osgi.service.event.Event
      • com.adobe.granite.workflow.event.WorkflowEvent

  • public class WorkflowEvent
extends org.osgi.service.event.Event
    WorkflowEvent provides an extension of Event that is used for propagating workflow related information as OSGI events.
